rows.label: tev046401_MSG0001
rows.name: I have many to thank for her. Not just Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0002
rows.name:
My daughter was stubborn. Her birth was hard.
We were both saved by Ma-non technology.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0003
rows.name:
And you helped with funeral ritual when Bazis
could not.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0004
rows.name:
This city is such good place.
Maybe even better than old home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0005
rows.name:
I think I will stay and raise Helna here.
I think I can with your help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0010
rows.name: Helna eats much. Sleeps much. But cries even more![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0011
rows.name:
She is such beautiful, healthy child.
It is hard work, but watching her grow is rewarding![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0012
rows.name:
Bazis helps watch our daughter when he returns
from hunt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046401_MSG0013
rows.name:
I could not be happier mother! To be surrounded by
such family and friends? Great Tree's Old Ones have
honored me with this destiny.[ST:wait ]
